# Return to Tetris

## Step to develop Tetris

- Setup the Game Loop
- Create the Grid
- Create the Blocks
- Move the Blocks
- Rotate the Blocks
- Checking for collisions
- Check for completed rows
- Game over
- Create User Interface
- Add Score
- Add Next Block
- Add sound

## Game Loop

- Event Handling
- Updating Position
- Drawing the objects

## Tools

- pygame
- Visual Studio Code
- Python
